      <title>智利反犯罪策划者因强奸指控辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chile-anti-crime-mastermind-steps-down-following-rape-allegation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利内政部副部长曼努埃尔·蒙萨尔维 (Manuel Monsalve) 因涉嫌强奸而接受调查的报道发布后辞职，这一令人震惊的进展导致政府失去了一位顶级打击犯罪的官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chile-anti-crime-mastermind-steps-down-following-rape-allegation</guid>
